    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An action-adventure with an interesting plot, where you will have to explore the world, develop the main character and fight with enemies. The story of the game takes place on a mysterious island with its own dark history and you will have to figure out what happened there.</strong> <br> <br><i>Key Features</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>1. The world of the game is not simple and combines different intriguing tasks that must be solved to move forward in the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271880/extras/04e317c5b9e7f7b1c551a4a0fb154ced.poster.avif?t=1761700154\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271880/extras/04e317c5b9e7f7b1c551a4a0fb154ced.webm?t=1761700154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271880/extras/04e317c5b9e7f7b1c551a4a0fb154ced.mp4?t=1761700154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. The protagonist is also constantly acquiring skills to overcome new locations, setting a dynamic tone for the game's narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. You will have to fight from simple enemies, to complex ones. Finding their weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271880/extras/2b20b44136b6f437c7a4806b8f88d4b6.poster.avif?t=1761700154\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271880/extras/2b20b44136b6f437c7a4806b8f88d4b6.webm?t=1761700154\" type=\"vi